data.description: **ASSUMABLE LOAN available at 3.125%! Contact for my details!** Prepare to be amazed because your next home awaits you! Nestled in a cul-de-sac, this gorgeous home will automatically feel like home when you enter the front porch. Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by high ceilings and gorgeous a gorgeous foyer. Walking forward, to the left you will have an office/study room. To the right, you will find the guest bathroom, as well as two spacious bedrooms, so spacious that king beds fit very nicely in both rooms. Continuing forward through the entryway, be amazed with the size and openness of the living/dining/kitchen. Such an amazing room to entertain in, or just relax and enjoy. The kitchen island is decorated with stone, while the ceilings have gorgeous wood beams. Through the living area, you will find the primary bedroom and bathroom. The coziness of this room will be felt immediately. The bathroom is, just wow! Dual sinks and large shower make this bathroom unreal. The backyard is a great size for anyone. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening wine on the covered patio. *Updates to the home* Water softener, ceiling fans added, extended driveway, backyard shed, epoxy garage floors, shelving and cabinets in garage, alarm system and Ring camera, trash bin fencing, 2 shatterproof glass doors (front and back), and stone landscaping.   Schedule your showing today because this gorgeous home won't last long.
